          "name": "README - Reports Endpoints",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": [""]
            },
            "description": "IMPORTANT: The Reports module is currently not implemented in the backend.\n\nExpected Report Types:\n1. Sales Report - Revenue, order statistics, popular items\n2. Reservation Report - Booking trends, table utilization\n3. Staff Performance Report - Orders handled, customer ratings\n4. Feedback Report - Customer satisfaction metrics, ratings analysis\n\nTo implement Reports, you would need:\n- Create report.controller.ts\n- Create report.service.ts\n- Create report.module.ts\n- Add DTOs for different report types\n- Implement aggregation queries for MongoDB\n\nBelow are example test cases for when the module is implemented."
          }
        }
